Fluent API Sandbox
------------------

This is a sandbox project to play around with some of the Java coding practices recommended by John Ferguson Smart at a recent PaddyPower Technology series event.

I've used this code to support a couple of blog posts:

The Builder Pattern: http://paddycorry.wordpress.com/2012/03/11/fluent-java-apis-i-the-builder-pattern/

A MockBuilder: http://paddycorry.wordpress.com/2012/07/02/fluent-java-apis-ii-the-mockbuilder-pattern/


http://paddycorry.wordpress.com